Hunting
[[File:Wolfdoom.jpg|thumb|[[Headshot]]!!!]]
[[File:Raptorjesus vs wolf.jpg|thumb|[[Raptor Jesus]] is a passionate [[wolf]] hunter, as well as being a champion anti-[[wolfaboo]] troll]]
'''Hunting''' is an activity that involves [[lulz|killing wild animals]] for [[O RLY|sport]] or just to [[did it for the lulz|have some fun]]. It may also be a way to earn livelihood [[Canada|for]] black person [[Finland|primitive]] [[Alaska|cultures]]. Hunting is viewed as murder by [[peta|uninformed retards]], but  is really a tradition for many families, and an effective way of keeping animal populations balanced. Dumbfucks known as poachers have ruined the reputation of ethical hunters, who follow all laws and care about the environment. A real hunter cares about the earth, and does his best to inform non-hunters about the good things hunting does for the planet. Unfortunately, there are [[retard|people]] known as poachers who make all hunters look like heartless fucks who kill things for no reason.
However, although it may seem like a [[ghey|manly]] thing to do at first sight, [[some argue]] that the will to go hunting stems from the [[conspiracy theory|fact]] that all hunters have been [[raep|violated]] [[over 9000|over 9000 times]] by [[incest|their relatives]] when they were [[pedophilia|kidz]].

